  "bib_entries": {
    "15242850": {
      "title": "Web technologies in industry hmi",
      "abstract": "This work deals with web technologies in industrial HMI systems. We created, designed and developed a HMI framework, which is based on web and cloud technologies. We also compared our system with available commercial solutions and described their advantages and disadvantages. The outcome of this work is not only a comparison of available solutions, but also the created framework and demo application. Our framework can be used for a cloud or private server industrial application. We made our framework to be easily adjust and upgrade. We developed a demo application in our framework, which is based on web technology and can be applied on mobile devices."
